    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "GlitchTip issue tracker",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 30
      },
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "GlitchTip is the Sentry-compatible error sink. Events ship from the worker via the DSN stored in `app_settings.sentry_dsn`.\n\n- **UI**: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)\n- **Org**: your GlitchTip org (mirrors `app_settings.glitchtip_triage_org_slug`) → **Project**: your project\n- **DSN**: `http://<public_key>@glitchtip-web:8000/1` (container-network form; browser-origin events should use `http://localhost:8080/1`)\n\nTrace → log → error correlation works when `sentry-trace` is propagated into OTEL spans. Click any error → **Open Trace** to jump into Tempo."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
